OL,3,CBanksy claims new statue in central
OL,4,CLondon
OL,6,FElusive artist Banksy has claimed a
OL,7,Fnew sculpture in central London of a
OL,8,Fman striding off a plinth with their
OL,9,Fface smothered by a billowing flag.
OL,11,FThe sculpture is on a plinth in
OL,12,FWaterloo Place, just off The Mall, and
OL,13,Fbears Banksy's signature.
OL,15,FIt is positioned on a traffic island
OL,16,Fin Pall Mall where Banksy said: "There
OL,17,Fwas a bit of a gap."
OL,19,FIt is situated close to statues of
OL,20,FEdward VII and Florence Nightingale,
OL,21,Fand the Crimean War Memorial.
OL,26,@xD@aOUyD@TO]
