OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1777914346
OL,3,CBanksy claims new statue in central
OL,4,CLondon
OL,6,FThe Press Association understands the
OL,7,Fartist revealed the unsolicited
OL,8,Fmonument at some point in the early
OL,9,Fhours of Wednesday, claiming it a day
OL,10,Flater.
OL,12,FBanksy, whose real name has never been
OL,13,Fofficially confirmed, has become
OL,14,Ffamous across the world for
OL,15,Fpolitically-charged murals, including
OL,16,F2002's Girl With Balloon, 2003's Love
OL,17,FIs In The Air, and 2004's Kissing
OL,18,FCoppers.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
