OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1777914346
OL,3,CBanksy claims new statue in central
OL,4,CLondon
OL,6,FBanksy claimed an artwork of two
OL,7,Ffigures that appeared on the side of a
OL,8,Fbuilding in Bayswater, London, in
OL,9,FDecember.
OL,11,FIn September, Banksy made headlines
OL,12,Fwith a mural depicting a protester
OL,13,Flying on the ground, holding a blood-
OL,14,Fspattered placard, while a judge, in a
OL,15,Fwig and gown, looms over him, wielding
OL,16,Fa gavel.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
