PN,40504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1777914346
OL,3,CBanksy claims new statue in central
OL,4,CLondon
OL,6,FThe painting appeared on an external
OL,7,Fwall of the Queen's Building, in the
OL,8,FRoyal Courts of Justice complex,
OL,9,Fhowever it was swiftly covered up and
OL,10,Fguarded by security staff, before work
OL,11,Fbegan to remove it.
OL,13,FThe art was interpreted by some as a
OL,14,Fcomment on the arrest of hundreds of
OL,15,Fpeople for supporting Palestine Action
OL,16,Fby holding up placards at protests.
